00:01:44,270 --> 00:01:48,540
Woman: we've yet to find
a working number
for his father.

7
00:01:48,542 --> 00:01:50,309
We've called friends.

8
00:01:50,311 --> 00:01:52,044
She never
talked about him,

9
00:01:52,046 --> 00:01:54,079
or even mentioned
any brothers or sisters.

10
00:01:54,081 --> 00:01:56,315
There's no relatives
on file.

11
00:01:58,017 --> 00:02:00,452
If we find
a working number
for his father,

12
