and he doesn't answer,
we'll leave a message.

13
00:02:02,289 --> 00:02:04,756
The state will handle
funeral arrangements.

14
00:02:04,758 --> 00:02:06,358
Man: check the file again.

15
00:02:06,360 --> 00:02:08,760
The boy has
a grandmother
in moorpark, colorado

16
00:02:08,762 --> 00:02:10,863
on his mother's side.

17
00:02:10,865 --> 00:02:13,031
I've been trying to call her,
but she hasn't been
answering the phone.

18
00:02:13,033 --> 00:02:14,500
I'll look again--

19
00:02:14,502 --> 00:02:17,703
just prepare
the foster care paperwork,

20
00:02:17,705 --> 00:02:20,439
in case she chooses
not to return our calls,

21
00:02:20,441 --> 00:02:23,442
or decides not to
take him in.

22
00:02:23,444 --> 00:02:27,112
With him turning 18
next summer, who knows
where he'll end up.

23
00:02:46,432 --> 00:02:49,268
[Truck horn honking]

24
