gonna heal.

864
01:41:47,734 --> 01:41:51,170
But something in
your eyes shows hope.

865
01:42:00,514 --> 01:42:02,748
So it's that obvious.

866
01:42:02,750 --> 01:42:07,253
To me, it is,
because I see you now.

867
01:42:09,690 --> 01:42:12,859
More than I think
others do.

868
01:42:18,332 --> 01:42:20,833
I love you so much.

869
01:42:34,081 --> 01:42:37,517
