was just crashing down
around me.

1004
01:59:14,714 --> 01:59:16,581
Talk to me.

1005
01:59:17,984 --> 01:59:20,886
- About what?
- About your father.

1006
01:59:20,888 --> 01:59:23,221
My father?

1007
01:59:26,826 --> 01:59:29,528
