Well...

1097
02:08:58,097 --> 02:09:01,666
When you wake up
in the morning,

1098
02:09:01,668 --> 02:09:05,269
it's the first thing
that comes to mind.

1099
02:09:05,271 --> 02:09:08,539
And when they're hurting,
you somehow feel it.

1100
02:09:10,509 --> 02:09:15,346
And when they're not around,
time does move slower.

1101
02:09:16,682 --> 02:09:19,350
Yeah, I'm definitely in love.

1102
02:09:19,352 --> 02:09:22,286
What happened?

1103
02:09:29,428 --> 02:09:32,430
Me...

1104
02:09:32,432 --> 02:09:35,099
Just me, running my mouth

1105
02:09:35,101 --> 02:09:38,269
before thinking about
what I'm saying.

1106
02:09:38,271 --> 02:09:42,440
Sometimes I build myself up,
and I tear myself down

1107
02:09:42,442 --> 02:09:44,509
all at the same time.

1108
02:09:49,214 --> 02:09:52,283
I don't know
what to do.

1109
02:09:52,285 --> 02:09:55,286
I don't know
how to deal with things.

1110
02:09:55,288 --> 02:09:57,288
Yes, you do.

1111
02:09:57,290 --> 02:10:01,259
Hey, you know how to
deal with things just fine.

1112
02:10:01,261 --> 02:10:04,862
You're here, aren't you?
You're dealing with this.

1113
