You're gonna
be okay.

1116
02:10:18,177 --> 02:10:21,412
But how do you deal
with being alone?

1117
02:10:23,348 --> 02:10:27,451
Well, you're never
really alone.

1118
02:10:29,388 --> 02:10:32,757
There's always someone there
to keep you hangin' on,

1119
02:10:32,759 --> 02:10:34,725
make life good.

1120
02:10:42,768 --> 02:10:44,902
Yeah.

1121
02:10:49,174 --> 02:10:52,944
You know, i...

1122
02:10:52,946 --> 02:10:55,513
It's crazy...

1123
02:10:55,515 --> 02:11:00,351
How something can just
change your life

1124
02:11:00,353 --> 02:11:02,653
and wake you up.

1125
02:11:02,655 --> 02:11:05,523
I mean, like really
wake you up.

1126
02:11:07,993 --> 02:11:10,494
I laid in that hospital bed
for days,

1127
02:11:10,496 --> 02:11:13,831
thinking the same thing
over and over again.

1128
02:11:15,467 --> 02:11:17,702
What?

1129
02:11:19,304 --> 02:11:22,974
If you don't create change,

1130
02:11:22,976 --> 02:11:26,344
