Come on, you should've
went to bed by now.

1143
02:12:56,269 --> 02:12:58,669
- Let's get you to bed.
- I got it.

1144
02:12:58,671 --> 02:13:00,938
I got it.

1145
02:13:03,208 --> 02:13:06,310
Did you go?

1146
02:13:06,312 --> 02:13:08,879
Yeah.

1147
02:13:08,881 --> 02:13:11,282
Good. I'm glad.

1148
02:13:17,089 --> 02:13:19,323
Me, too.

1149
02:14:05,604 --> 02:14:07,505
- Hey.
- Aldo.

1150
02:14:11,043 --> 02:14:13,677
- I can't...
- I know.

1151
02:14:14,946 --> 02:14:17,114
But maybe you can call me
from time to time,

1152
02:14:17,116 --> 02:14:19,583
just to
check up on me
if you want.

1153
02:14:19,585 --> 02:14:23,087
Yeah, I'd like that.

1154
02:14:24,589 --> 02:14:26,824
Here's my cell.

1155
02:14:30,962 --> 02:14:33,097
Thanks.

1156
02:15:28,954 --> 02:15:30,754
[Glass shattering]

1157
02:15:30,756 --> 02:15:32,923
mrs. Wallace?

1158
02:15:50,709 --> 02:15:54,245
