ms. Shirley doyle.

1171
02:17:18,830 --> 02:17:21,332
I'm so sorry.

1172
02:18:23,094 --> 02:18:25,162
You should go in there.

1173
02:19:14,679 --> 02:19:16,547
[Moaning]

1174
02:19:54,753 --> 02:19:56,754
aldo?

1175
02:19:58,423 --> 02:20:00,491
Grandma.

1176
02:20:02,093 --> 02:20:04,828
Is your father
out there?

1177
02:20:07,766 --> 02:20:11,168
Yeah. Everyone's here.

1178
02:20:14,773 --> 02:20:16,740
How are you feelin'?

1179
02:20:18,610 --> 02:20:20,911
Not good,

1180
02:20:20,913 --> 02:20:24,047
